This node.js installation is used to send push notifications to all authenticated users of the chat in the "Bahnhofsfotos" App.

Change the name of the file firebase-messgeing-sw Template.js to firebase-messaging-sw.js and insert your SenderID from the firebase-Project.

You can find a description, how to use it here: 
https://firebase.google.com/docs/functions/get-started

The basecode is from the codelabs-project friendly_chat from Google:
https://github.com/firebase/friendlychat
